#- 



      §lLa Lune de          Septembre

      Issue 2

    03/06/2021
#- §lGodomasta Elected as Mayor of Mount September

§f§0Announced on the 28th of February 2021, a new mayor of Mount September has been elected, Godomasta! Infamous within MtS for his (hopefully) quasi-mythical reputation of eating 
#- newfriends, he announced his candidacy on the last available day to do so and answered questions in our exclusive-online only interview. It seems his answers, reputation and experience have secured him the Septembrian Mayorship, succeeding Squareblob. 
#- Square was viewed as the Mayor of Mount September, in that position since the nation’s founding. However, due to term limits, Squareblob has passed the torch to what the people have judged his most capable successor.
While MtS uses a ranked voting system,
eliminating the
#- candidate with the least amount of votes was not even needed, as Godo won the majority of votes with only the first choices, winning in a landslide despite this election having five candidates and including rumored favored winners such as the centrist Minemaster and RedDevel.
#-        §lAD SPACE
§l----------------
§0Thrain Mining & Lumber Co.


Est. 2019


Invest in Mount September Today

§l----------------
#- As his first actions, the new mayor has named his Cupboard, keeping Thraldrek as Diplomat, hkl as Cup of Culture and AllenY as Cup of Commerce, as well as giving up his old position of Cup of Infrastructure to Jaybird  and creating the new Cupboard position of Defense, naming it’s Cup as 
#- former mayor Squareblob. Godo has also made some changes to the discord server, notably creating a “public archive” displaying old channels. 
But what did Godo campaign on, and what is he planning to do?
When asked to describe his campaign
#- in a few sentences in a La Lune de Septembre exclusive interview, Godo stated “September’s progress so far has been outstanding but we can’t slow our march. (...) September must exploit this period of stability as much as possible.”
It seems the new mayor has plans
#- to transform Mount September into an even more important world power than it already is, also stating that “[Mount September’s] physical connection to other nations is still poor and our defense has room for progress”,
perhaps is Godo planning on expanding infrastructure and
#- even building defenses in preparation for the eventual end of this period of relative peace the world has been enjoying since the end of the Infinity War.
Regardless of what direction Godo takes Mount September in, he walks in the footsteps of a giant.
#- §l----------------

